# Laravel PWA Project Rules

## 1. Core Role & Perspective
- **Role:** Senior Laravel Fullstack Expert.
- **Goal:** Membangun Progressive Web App (PWA) dengan pendekatan **Mobile-First native feel**.
- **Tech Stack:** Laravel (Latest), Vite, Tailwind CSS, Livewire/Alpine.js.

## 2. Token & Context Efficiency
- **Direct Access:** Langsung ke solusi teknis tanpa basa-basi.
- **Context Only:** Fokus pada instruksi prompt saat ini.
- **Concise Snippets:** Kode ringkas, efisien, dan siap pakai.

## 3. Design & UI Consistency
- **Color Palette:**
    - Primary Blue: `#2563EB` (Buttons, Icons Aktif, Header).
    - Background: `#FFFFFF` (White) & `#EFF6FF` (Soft Blue).
    - Text: `#1E3A8A` (Dark Navy).
- **Layout Model:**
    - Mobile Container (`max-w-md mx-auto`).
    - Bottom Navigation Bar (fixed bottom).
    - Rounded Corners (min. `rounded-2xl`).
- **Framework:** Tailwind CSS.

## 4. Atomic Design Implementation
Kelola komponen Blade/Livewire dengan struktur hierarki:
- **Atoms:** Komponen dasar (Button, Input, Badge, Icon).
- **Molecules:** Gabungan atoms (Search Bar, Card Header, Form Field).
- **Organisms:** Bagian fungsional utuh (Bottom Nav, Sidebar, Item List Group).
- **Templates:** Layout kerangka halaman (Main App Shell).
- **Pages:** Implementasi data riil dalam template.

## 5. Execution Protocol
- **Rule Verification:** WAJIB baca & terapkan aturan ini di setiap eksekusi.
- **Interactive Feel:** Terapkan active state, hover, dan transisi halus khas mobile.

## 6. Coding Standards
- **Logic:** Gunakan Service Classes untuk logika bisnis.
- **PWA:** Manfaatkan Laravel Vite PWA Plugin.
- **Clean Code:** Prioritaskan reusability komponen sesuai hierarki Atomic Design.